high_descs: Turn to the left and go to the counter across the room.
Pick up the rightmost box of tissues that is on the counter.
Turn to the right, go forward, hang a right and go to the toilet.
Put the box of tissues on the back of the toilet.
Turn to the right, go to the wall, hang a right and go to the counter.
Pick up the leftmost box of tissues that is on the counter.
Turn to the right, go forward, hang a right and go to the toilet.
Put the box of tissues on the back of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Put two boxes of tissues on the back of the toilet.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the counter.
Pick up the tissue box to the left of the toilet paper roll.
Turn around, walk to the toilet, and look at the back of the toilet.
Put the tissue box down on the back of the toilet.
Walk back over to the counter to the right of the door.
Pick up the tissue box on the left.
Walk back over to face the back of the toilet.
Put the tissue box down on the back of the toilet behind the first box of tissues.
anns.task_desc: To move two tissue boxes to the back of the toilet.

high_descs: Go left and face the counter with tissue boxes on it.
Pick up the tissue box on the right.
Turn around and face the toilet.
Put the tissue box on the back of the toilet.
Turn around to face the white counter.
Pick the tissue box on the left up from the counter.
Turn around to face the toilet.
Put the tissue box down on the back of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Put two tissue boxes on the back of the toilet.
